data.description: Welcome to the vibrant area of South Austin! Presenting to you an exceptional two-story home at 6109 Mary Lewis Dr, boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a versatile office space. This thoughtfully designed residence provides a perfect combination of spaciousness, functionality, and privacy.    Upon entering the home, you'll be captivated by the open floor plan that seamlessly connects the main living areas. The downstairs area comprises 3 bedrooms, each offering comfortable and private retreats for family members or guests. Additionally, there's a dedicated office space, providing a quiet environment for work or study.    As you make your way upstairs, you'll be delighted to find a game room, perfect for leisurely activities or entertaining friends and family. Accompanied by a bedroom and bathroom, this space offers versatility and additional privacy, making it an ideal setup for various lifestyles.    Throughout the home, beautiful touches and modern finishes are evident, adding a touch of sophistication to every room. The carefully selected materials and design choices highlight the attention to detail that went into crafting this splendid residence.    Located in the coveted South Austin area, this home provides easy access to local amenities, renowned schools, and entertainment options. Whether you're looking to relax, work, or entertain, 6109 Mary Lewis Dr offers a delightful sanctuary that caters to your every need.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fabulous property in a sought-after location. Schedule a tour today and experience the comfort and convenience this South Austin home has to offer!
